<div class="panels_pane panel-pane pane-custom pane-2" >
  
      <h2 class="pane-title">Benefits of Membership</h2>
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <ul>
<li>Use of PGC/PACT contracts for professional productions;</li>
<li>Advice on issues including: negotiating contracts, artists&#39; rights and copyright;</li>
<li>Member newsletter including lists of opportunities for playwrights;</li>
<li>Access to the Canada Council Readings Program;</li>
<li>And more.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Memberships available for playwrights of all experience levels</h3>
<div class="block-button"><a href="/membership">Learn More</a></div>
